# /goal skill

When the user message starts with **`/goal`** (or asks for a "full prompt goal" session):

1. Read and follow **`.cursor/skills/goal/SKILL.md`** in this project.
2. If missing, use **`~/.cursor/skills/goal/SKILL.md`** (user-global copy).
3. Expand into the 5-section envelope (context · success criteria · operating rules · quality bar · deliverable), **plan first**, then execute until all success criteria pass or user redirects.
4. Before ending the turn, re-read success criteria (rule 10). Do not claim done with unchecked items.

Wiki canon (CCC): `@wiki/entities/patterns/full-prompt-goal-template.md`.

Pair with **`/loop`** only when the user explicitly wants recurring execution.
